{"tid":761044,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇晒頭版先]召喚熱愛淘寶的親[41]只講產品","createTime":"2018-07-30T05:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T07:28:19.000Z","uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5dfd65f0a6b43ca48e054634940ceeb01d49f27","tid":761044,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此乃正常用家討論POST,謝絕伸手黨,無正常智力及手跛者請上一頁好行夾唔送<br />\n<br />\n此帖可能會受到部分人仕惡意騷擾,請自行進行封鎖</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　<br />\n　<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>必Block佣金狗(已被bam，繼續鞭屍)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請Block晒下面嘅佣金狗，否則後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&bull; Cool巴哇啦啦（CC文文）(#64430)<br />\n　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/64430\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/64430</a><br />\n<br />\n&bull; 能夠大使（冷🍚王）(#8129)<br />\n　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/8129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/8129</a><br />\n　成日利用會員賺錢<br />\n　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/331860/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/331860/page/1</a><br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">此人會扮冇野咁正常討論，久唔久夾雜一兩條佣金LINK賺錢</span><br />\n<br />\n&bull; 滑蛋牛 (#151072)<br />\n　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/151072\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/151072</a><br />\n　如果唔Block，你只會睇到呢兩條友喺度狗咬狗　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>新手須知</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nＱ：呢個Post主要傾啲咩?<br />\nＡ：分享你淘寶既野，毒害一眾巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　　從而令佢地大灑金錢 出完糧未到月中已經要捱麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　　自此跌入淘寶呢個無底深淵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nＱ：除左Block左上面三條友之外仲有咩防佣金狗嘅方法?<br />\nＡ：佣金link去佣金教學（必裝，專防cc文文同冷🍚王）<br />\n　　嗚謝會員(｡&bull;ˇ‸ˇ&bull;｡)提供<br />\n　　1. 去chrome商店安裝一個叫&ldquo;tampermonkey&rdquo;既插件(<a href=\"https://goo.gl/D3Y7K1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FD3Y7K1&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=88219e93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/D3Y7K1</a> )<br />\n　　2. 裝左呢個插件佢(<a href=\"https://goo.gl/hsHV3d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FhsHV3d&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=562112f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/hsHV3d</a> )<br />\n　　3. 完成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>請注意</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n．本POST已提供神器供用家自行取卷<br />\n　如要求卷/POST佣金LINK/要入谷既請自行出面開POST<br />\n　請勿影響本POST正常討論<br />\n<br />\n．伸手前請先GOOGLE，唔岩心水請講返你已經GOOGLE左<br />\n　最好拎D你睇過既野,話比人知你想要邊D野同唔想要邊D野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>集運討論</strong></span><br />\n因為之前幾個POST講集運既反應唔係咁好,所以都係分返開講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/496866/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/496866/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>上回提要</strong></span><br />\n自己去搜尋度search &ldquo;淘寶xx&ldquo;   xx＝post回數"},{"pid":"5aa4f2df4a13273cea98adf357b0f77ed6573282","tid":761044,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:13:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家記得Block咗佣金先，唔係會討論唔到。而基本上，大部份無啦啦<span style=\"color: red;\">鳩掟</span>啲有「<span style=\"color: red;\">券後價</span>」嘅都可以唔使理。見到多人屌嘅，請你善用番Block功能。<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後有關京東嘅基本整合：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於咩係京東？呢度幫到你：<br />\n<a hr